    <announcement text="MoreCore Ruleset (Version 1.51 20190428). This generic ruleset adds features and flexibility allowing you to play more game systems. \r\nThis ruleset coded by damned and ianmward. Additional thanks to Trenloe, mcortez, superteddy57 and others for their assistance along the way. This incorporates dice rolling extensions from Ikael, DMFirmy, Frostbyte, Sibelius, Trenloe, Imiri, Myrddin, rstrahan, ahoggya, superteddy57, mcortez, David Stitt, thwright, trobadork, SmileyMan, damned and ianmward.\r\nDicePool and much other goodness by ianmward.\r\nRoll Parameters by mcortez.\r\nClick link for User Guide" icon="morecorelogo" font="emotefont" link="http://www.diehard-gaming.com"/> 

	<announcement text="Help grow MoreCore. If you would like to support MoreCore you can do so in the following ways:\r\n* Use MoreCore and spread the word about the systems you are playing\r\n* Use MoreCore and upload and share Character sheets (and even campaigns) and instructions for the systems you are playing\r\n* Creating new Rolls for MoreCore and allowing them to be included into MoreCore\r\n* Creating new Theme Extensions for MoreCore and sharing them on the forums\r\n* If you would like to make a donation to help feed my RPG habit you can donate at PayPal.me/fgdamned" icon="handshake" font="oocfont" link="https://www.paypal.me/fgdamned"/> 

